import { Route, Switch } from "react-router-dom"
import Login from "./Login"
import SignUp from "./SignUp"

const App=()=>{
  return(
    <>
      <Switch>

        <Route path="/login" exact component={()=><Login/>}/>
        <Route path="/signup" exact component={()=><SignUp/>}/>
      </Switch>
    </>
  )
}
export default App
